data.description: Welcome home to this beautifully renovated residence sitting on over an acre of fenced in land. Complete with brand new features including a New hot Water Heater, Interior Paint, and Luxury Vinyl Plank flooring throughout the home. Enjoy this modern touch complemented with brand New Interior Doors, Newly remodeled Bathrooms and Kitchen, recently upgraded Plumbing and Stainless steel appliances! This home is equipped with a new 200 amp service as well as a Septic tank, your own Well for convenience including a water filtration system, this home combines both style and functionality.
